Files
=====

makebuild.sh is only used by me to create the build for distribution.
You should only have this file if you checked out the git repo.


djvu2pdf INSTALL
================

 Copy the djvu2pdf shell script in one of your PATH directories and make it
 executable.

  $ chmod +x djvu2pdf && mv djvu2pdf ~/bin

 To install the manpage, copy it in your man1 directory.

  # mv djvu2pdf.1.gz /usr/man/man1
